headline.print_headline: Yahoo Options Popular Ahead of Alibaba IPO
headline.main: Yahoo Options Popular Ahead of Alibaba IPO

lead_paragraph: Alibaba Group Holding Ltd's shares do not begin trading until Friday, so investors hungry for a bite of the Chinese e-commerce giant have turned their attention to Yahoo Inc's options in recent days.
